Based on your HICSS formatting needs and priority on emphasizing your **BEND-guided counterspeech generation** and **LLM-as-judge evaluation**, here‚Äôs a fully shortened, citation-dense version of your literature review (\~900‚Äì950 words). I‚Äôve merged references, removed redundancy, and emphasized novelty clearly.

