**Usage:**
1. Choose the manoeuvre that matches your strategy.
2. Paste the hateful tweet and optional context into the template.
3. Run it through your LLM fine‚Äëtuned model.
4. The model returns a single, ready‚Äëto‚Äëpost counter‚Äëtweet aligned with Carley‚Äôs BEND framework.


